H0.text: What French word prefixes couture, cuisine and ecole meaning high quality or advanced. Grande

H1.text: What French word prefixes couture, cuisine and ecole meaning high quality or advanced. Belle

H2.text: What French word prefixes couture, cuisine and ecole meaning high quality or advanced. Fine

H3.text: What French word prefixes couture, cuisine and ecole meaning high quality or advanced. Haute

A4.text: The English term haute couture was borrowed from French, where it literally means 'high sewing' or 'high dressmaking'.
